headline: Expedia Group to Webcast Third Quarter 2025 Results on November 6, 2025
summary: SEATTLE, October 02, 2025--Expedia Group (NASDAQ: EXPE) will report its third quarter 2025 results for the period ended September 30, 2025, on Thursday, November 6, 2025 via an earnings release and accompanying webcast. These items will be available in the Investor Relations section of the company’s corporate website at http://ir.expediagroup.com.
